snippet.title: Rainbow Balloonicorn
snippet.description:
I have autism and like most people on the autism spectrum, I have a special interest. My special interest is balloons. Balloons are my safe-space and comfort. Balloons have been a part of my life since childhood.  

I have converted my barn into a controlled multisensory environment (MSE) to help me cope with autism.

snippet.title: ColdFusion
snippet.description:
Hi, my name is Dagogo Altraide and I create and narrate all the videos on here.
This channel aims to let you experience the cutting edge of the world around us in a relaxed atmosphere.
Learn the captivating stories about how our world came to be and also learn what's happening in the cutting edge today.
